 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">CRISPR holds=
 enormous potential, but given its relative nascency, regulatory hurdles, a=
nd safety considerations, its application in actual treatments has remained=
 limited to clinical trials, until now.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(64, 64, 6=
4); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>CASGEVY&=
